        {
            "_id": "vbDdsrV2yN5pNuLn",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Possess Creature",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The retail phantasm attempts to possess an adjacent corporeal creature. This has the same effect as the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.spells.Item.Possession] spell (DC 18), except the duration is [[/gmr 1d4 #hours]]{1d4 hours}, and since the retail phantasm doesn't have a physical body, it's unaffected by that restriction of the spell. If the target is an employee of the same company as the retail phantasm, the DC is 22.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "PIa0c70i9D1kbTQN",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Unpaid Overtime",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The retail phantasm touches an adjacent creature, causing the weight of years of toil to overcome them at once. The creature must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:18] save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is enfeebled 1 for 24 hours and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Fatigued].</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is enfeebled 1 for 24 hours, fatigued, and falls @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Unconscious]. If it's still unconscious after 1 minute, it wakes up automatically.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "curse",
                        "divine"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        }
